text: Last Year Was Complicated
Fuck it. I'm gonna tell you the title.
.@ToveLo @BigSean @tydollasign @alleniverson thank you for being apart of this body of work.
Well maybe I've said too much tonight... Instagram tomorrow I reveal the album cover and title.
And the title of my new album coming out June 10th is..
Comfortable
Unhinged
Under You
Don't Make Me Choose
The Difference
Good Girls
Bacon
Touch
Chainsaw
Close
Champagne Problems
Voodoo
So I might as well tell you the title of each track right..
The track listing will be up tomorrow night too. With the pre sale of the album... Every song is so personal and meaningful to me..
The first song you're gonna hear tomorrow night is about how I literally can't open up and be vulnerable with someone..
But I know it's important that I do it. I want to be an open book in my art..
Shit is too real sometimes... Reliving some of these real life experiences through this music is hard.
It then became very clear what this thing would be about... And that I would need to dig really deep.
When I first started making I thought I knew what it would be about... Then I had a breakup.
Tomorrow night I'm gonna show the world the first single.
I've been making this record for a year and a half... Pouring everything I have into it.
A lot on my mind tonight...
https://t.co/GTYM7ut6q9
